s."}, {"role": "user", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "You are examining a polling-place plan for a county with roughly 80 precincts and 18 opened polling places. No map is provided \u2014 use the structured tools to inspect assignments and adjacency.\n\nA polling place's *service area* is the set of precincts currently assigned to it.\n\nA service area is **non-contiguous** when the precincts assigned to that polling place split into two or more connected components on the precinct adjacency graph (the get_precinct_adjacency tool returns this graph).\n\nFor every opened polling place whose service area is non-contiguous, report it together with a brief reason explaining the evidence. If every service area is contiguous, return an empty list.\n\nRespond with ONLY a JSON object of the form:\n  {\"split_sites\": [\n    {\"index\": <i>, \"reason\": \"<short justification>\"},\n    ...\n  ]}\nEach `reason` should briefly state which connected components you found and which precincts populate them. Keep each reason under 40 words. Do not include any other text outside the JSON."}]}, {"role": "assistant", "annotations": [], "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_7AGvu8UibDehMmud2Ng45Uh1", "function": {"arguments": "{\"opened_only\": true}", "name": "list_sites"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_hWGFWq0a2VnXYlsvPqQbq14g", "function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "get_current_assignments"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_BqFNv1iY7N7v0eBjLukVn3xI", "function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "get_precinct_adjacency"}, "type": "function"}]}, {"role": "tool", "tool_call_id": "call_7AGvu8UibDehMmud2Ng45Uh1", "content": "[{\"index\": 1, \"x\": 7.991070668320852, \"y\": 3.3547876691596543, \"type\": \"church\", \"capacity\": 3500, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 2999}, {\"index\": 2, \"x\": 5.895061094620223, \"y\": 1.235360890349781, \"type\": \"church\", \"capacity\": 3500, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 2788}, {\"index\": 3, \"x\": 5.797336599735673, \"y\": 4.6, \"type\": \"community_cent