ompute connected components on an opened site's assigned-precinct subgraph: more than one component means a non-contiguous service area.\"}"}, {"content": "{\"split_sites\":[{\"index\":0,\"reason\":\"Two separate blue patches on west side: mid-west (precincts 68,71) and southwest (74,77). Adjacency among site-0 precincts splits into two components.\"},{\"index\":23,\"reason\":\"Same tan color appears in northwest and north-central patches. Site 23 precincts split into west cluster (36,42,49,51,55,64,73) and isolated east patch (59,65) by adjacency.\"},{\"index\":29,\"reason\":\"Gray area splits into northeast block and a smaller east-central patch near y\u22487.4. Site 29 precincts form components {39,41,44,48,54,79} and {76}.\"},{\"index\":30,\"reason\":\"Light-gray service area has west-central patch and separate far-left upper patch. Site 30 precincts split into {34,45,50,69} and isolated precinct 73 by adjacency.\"},{\"index\":33,\"reason\":\"Olive/yellow-green appears southwest and far south-central. Site 33 precincts split into main cluster {1,4,5,8,10,66,75} and isolated precinct 74.\"},{\"index\":39,\"reason\":\"Cyan service area has broad south-central region plus detached small inner patch near (5.1,1.7). Site 39 precincts are components {14,16,67,70} and isolated precinct 22.\"}]}", "role": "assistant", "annotations": []}]}}
{"row_id": 21, "pair_id": "contiguity_med_07", "archetype": "contiguity", "difficulty": "med", "task": "identify", "renderer": "v2_no_markers", "prompt": "tools_only", "model": "openai_vlm_tools:gpt-5.4", "raw_response": "{\"split_sites\":[{\"index\":4,\"reason\":\"Two components: {0,4,8,14} and isolated {74}; precinct 74 only touches 11,21,69,76, all assigned elsewhere.\"},{\"index\":5,\"reason\":\"Two components: {12,16,22,25,29,31,33} and isolated {24}; precinct 24 connects only to 12,20,23,33,67,71, none assigned to site 5.\"},{\"index\":8,\"reason\":\"Two components: {28,30,32,53,57} and isolated {26}; precinct 26 touches 27,28,48,50,57, but no adjacent precinct except 28 shares site 8.\"},{\"index\":13,\"reason\":\"Two components: {35,36,37,42,47,52,59,65} and isolated {51}; precinct 51 only touches 40,58,60,62,66,68, all assigned elsewhere.\"},{\"index\":14,\"reason\":\"Two components: {38,45,54,55,64} and isolated {34}; precinct 34 only touches 38,41,43,46,55, none assigned to site 14.\"},{\"index\":16,\"reason\":\"Two components: {34,41,43,46,63,73} and isolated {55}; precinct 55 touches 34,38,45,46,54, with neighboring precincts assigned to sites 14 or 16 only.\"},{\"index\":19,\"reason\":\"Two components: {39,48,49,50,61} and isolated {68}; precinct 68 only touches 40 and 66, both assigned to site 15.\"},{\"index\":27,\"reason\":\"Two components: {40,51,56,58,60} and isolated {68}; precinct 68 only touches 40 and 66, assigned to sites 27 and 15, leaving 68 disconnected.\"},{\"index\":37,\"reason\":\"Three components: {23,27,71}, isolated {72}, and isolated {34}; precinct 72 touches only 67,71; precinct 34 is elsewhere and not adjacent to other site-37 precincts.\"}]}", "parsed_answer": {"split_sites": [4, 5, 8, 13, 14, 16, 19, 27, 37], "reasons": {"4": "Two components: {0,4,8,14} and isolated {74}; precinct 74 only touches 11,21,69,76, all assigned elsewhere.", "5": "Two components: {12,16,22,25,29,31,33} and isolated {24}; precinct 24 connects only to 12,20,23,33,67,71, none assigned to site 5.", "8": "Two components: {28,30,32,53,57} and isolated {26}; precinct 26 touches 27,28,48,50,57, but no adjacent precinct except 28 shares site 8.", "13": "Two components: {35,36,37,42,47,52,59,65} and isolated {51}; precinct 51 only touches 40,58,60,62,66,68, all assigned elsewhere.", "14": "Two components: {38,45,54,55,64} and isolated {34}; precinct 34 only touches 38,41,43,46,55, none assigned to site 14.", "16": "Two components: {34,41,43,46,63,73} and isolated {55}; precinct 55 touches 34,38,45,46,54, with neighboring precincts assigned to sites 14 or 16 only.", "19": "Two components: {39,48,49,50,61} and isolated {68}; precinct 68 only touches 40 and 66, both assigned to site 15.", "27": "Two components: {40,51,56,58,60} and isolated {68}; precinct 68 only touches 40 and 66, assigned to sites 27 and 15, leaving 68 disconnected.", "37": "Three components: {23,27,71}, isolated {72}, and isolated {34}; precinct 72 touches only 67,71; precinct 34 is elsewhere and not adjacent to other site-37 precincts."}}, "score": 0.0, "secondary_scores": {"pred_size": 9.0, "truth_size": 1.0, "fp_count": 9.0, "fn_count": 1.0, "tp_count": 0.0, "precision": 0.0, "recall": 0.0}, "tool_calls": 3, "tool_call_log": [{"name": "list_sites", "arguments": "{\"opened_only\": true}", "result_preview": "[{\"index\": 2, \"x\": 0.5696333348837019, \"y\": 1.207229999557637, \"type\": \"library\", \"capacity\": 3000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 2164}, {\"index\": 4, \"x\": 2.2075920324032348, \"y\": 3.081491965962308, \"type\":"}, {"name": "get_current_assignments", "arguments": "{}", "result_preview": "{\"n_precincts\": 80, \"n_returned\": 80, \"assignments\": [{\"precinct\": 0, \"x\": 2.156250508204456, \"y\": 2.731456635930461, \"voters\": 699, \"assigned_site\": 4, \"assigned_distance\": 0.3537805596376913, \"weigh"}, {"name": "get_precinct_adjacency", "arguments": "{}", "result_preview": "{\"n_precincts\": 80, \"neighbors\": [[4, 5, 8, 9, 14], [2, 5, 9, 44, 63, 73], [1, 5, 73, 77], [6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 35, 44], [0, 5, 11, 14, 70, 74, 75, 76], [0, 1, 2, 4, 9, 70, 77], [3, 7, 8, 14], [3, 6, 10, "}], "elapsed_sec": 7.43921422958374, "error": "", "api_metadata": {"usage": {"completion_tokens": 530, "prompt_tokens": 12846, "total_tokens": 13376, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 0, "rejected_prediction_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 0}}, "finish_reason": "stop", "model_resolved": "gpt-5.4-2026-03-05", "system_fingerprint": null, "request_id": "chatcmpl-Ddfk7WDIoMsOnMzFbShEFEJZK1KZX", "n_turns": 2, "per_turn_finish_reasons": ["tool_calls", "stop"], "conversation": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are a careful analyst examining a polling-place plan for a county.  Use the structured tools below as needed to answer the user's question.\n\nTools available:\n  list_sites(opened_only) \u2014 candidate or opened polling places (index, location in km, capacity, type, opened/closed status, and current voter load if opened).\n  get_precinct_centroids(precinct_indices) \u2014 centroid coordinates in km of the requested precincts (or all precincts if `precinct_indices` is omitted).\n  get_precinct_adjacency() \u2014 for each precinct, the indices of its spatially-adjacent precincts (4-connected on the rasterised Voronoi map). Useful for connectivity questions.\n  get_current_assignments(precinct_indices) \u2014 for each precinct, the polling place it is currently assigned to, plus the assigned travel distance. Omit `precinct_indices` for all.\n  get_assigned_site_at(x, y) \u2014 the polling place currently serving the precinct that contains coordinate (x, y).\n\nThe map is approximately 0\u201310 km on each axis, and there are roughly 80 precincts and 18 opened polling places. When you have enough information to answer, respond in the format the user requests."}, {"role": "user", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "You are examining a polling-place plan for a county with roughly 80 precincts and 18 opened polling places. No map is provided \u2014 use the structured tools to inspect assignments and adjacency.\n\nA polling place's *service area* is the set of precincts currently assigned to it.\n\nA service area is **non-contiguous** when the precincts assigned to that polling place split into two or more connected components on the precinct adjacency graph (the get_precinct_adjacency tool returns this graph).\n\nFor every opened polling place whose service area is non-contiguous, report it together with a brief reason explaining the evidence. If every service area is contiguous, return an empty list.\n\nRespond with ONLY a JSON object of the form:\n  {\"split_sites\": [\n    {\"index\": <i>, \"reason\": \"<short justification>\"},\n    ...\n  ]}\nEach `reason` should briefly state which connected components you found and which precincts populate them. Keep each reason under 40 words. Do not include any other text outside the JSON."}]}, {"role": "assistant", "annotations": [], "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_22oJkjIOq0ZlnV8SEfNwMx2S", "function": {"arguments": "{\"opened_only\": true}", "name": "list_sites"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_uc4Ydr8YhaRDk84fVIzZPvG5", "function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "get_current_assignments"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_usFioznxa15N6aRFkL7zdwzy", "function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "get_precinct_adjacency"}, "type": "function"}]}, {"role": "tool", "tool_call_id": "call_22oJkjIOq0ZlnV8SEfNwMx2S", "content": "[{\"index\": 2, \"x\": 0.5696333348837019, \"y\": 1.207229999557637, \"type\": \"library\", \"capacity\": 3000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 2164}, {\"index\": 4, \"x\": 2.2075920324032348, \"y\": 3.081491965962308, \"type\": \"library\", \"capacity\": 3000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 2876}, {\"index\": 5, \"x\": 6.027234849005439, \"y\": 2.674764175270805, \"type\": \"library\", \"capacity\": 3000, \"opened\": true, \"load\":