{"row_id": 45, "pair_id": "contiguity_med_15", "archetype": "contiguity", "difficulty": "med", "task": "identify", "renderer": "v2_no_markers", "prompt": "tools_only", "model": "openai_vlm_tools:gpt-5.4", "raw_response": "{\"split_sites\":[{\"index\":0,\"reason\":\"Two components: {0,1,4,5,6,8,9,10,11,77} and isolated {71}; precinct 71 borders only 70,77,79, none assigned to site 0.\"},{\"index\":1,\"reason\":\"Two components: {19} and isolated {79}; 79 is adjacent only to 71,72,77, none assigned to site 1.\"},{\"index\":37,\"reason\":\"Two components: {7,41} and isolated {70}; precinct 70 borders 0,7,8,71,77, all assigned elsewhere except 7.\"},{\"index\":39,\"reason\":\"Two components: {67,75,76} and isolated {32}; precinct 32 touches 26,27,28,30,67,76, but none of those except 67/76 are assigned to site 39, leaving 32 disconnected.\"}]}", "parsed_answer": {"split_sites": [0, 1, 37, 39], "reasons": {"0": "Two components: {0,1,4,5,6,8,9,10,11,77} and isolated {71}; precinct 71 borders only 70,77,79, none assigned to site 0.", "1": "Two components: {19} and isolated {79}; 79 is adjacent only to 71,72,77, none assigned to site 1.", "37": "Two components: {7,41} and isolated {70}; precinct 70 borders 0,7,8,71,77, all assigned elsewhere except 7.", "39": "Two components: {67,75,76} and isolated {32}; precinct 32 touches 26,27,28,30,67,76, but none of those except 67/76 are assigned to site 39, leaving 32 disconnected."}}, "score": 0.4, "secondary_scores": {"pred_size": 4.0, "truth_size": 1.0, "fp_count": 3.0, "fn_count": 0.0, "tp_count": 1.0, "precision": 0.25, "recall": 1.0}, "tool_calls": 3, "tool_call_log": [{"name": "list_sites", "arguments": "{\"opened_only\": true}", "result_preview": "[{\"index\": 0, \"x\": 2.534889222339105, \"y\": 2.747697619471602, \"type\": \"school\", \"capacity\": 5000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 4964}, {\"index\": 1, \"x\": 3.4284490208398757, \"y\": 1.2193280442594487, \"type\": "}, {"name": "get_current_assignments", "arguments": "{}", "result_preview": "{\"n_precincts\": 80, \"n_returned\": 80, \"assignments\": [{\"precinct\": 0, \"x\": 1.4813651591289798, \"y\": 3.2809882747068815, \"voters\": 596, \"assigned_site\": 0, \"assigned_distance\": 1.180809838510861, \"weig"}, {"name": "get_precinct_adjacency", "arguments": "{}", "result_preview": "{\"n_precincts\": 80, \"neighbors\": [[7, 8, 9, 11, 12, 70], [5, 6, 9, 10, 11], [7, 12, 41, 58, 59, 62], [9, 10, 12, 17, 62], [5, 6, 10, 16, 17, 19], [1, 4, 6, 8, 11, 19, 72, 77], [1, 4, 5, 10], [0, 2, 12"}], "elapsed_sec": 5.179781198501587, "error": "", "api_metadata": {"usage": {"completion_tokens": 267, "prompt_tokens": 12830, "total_tokens": 13097, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 0, "rejected_prediction_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 0}}, "finish_reason": "stop", "model_resolved": "gpt-5.4-2026-03-05", "system_fingerprint": null, "request_id": "chatcmpl-Ddfmq2myfR6Chvq67mUVq1HQhzBCu", "n_turns": 2, "per_turn_finish_reasons": ["tool_calls", "stop"], "conversation": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are a careful analyst examining a polling-place plan for a county.  Use the structured tools below as needed to answer the user's question.\n\nTools available:\n  list_sites(opened_only) \u2014 candidate or opened polling places (index, location in km, capacity, type, opened/closed status, and current voter load if opened).\n  get_precinct_centroids(precinct_indices) \u2014 centroid coordinates in km of the requested precincts (or all precincts if `precinct_indices` is omitted).\n  get_precinct_adjacency() \u2014 for each precinct, the indices of its spatially-adjacent precincts (4-connected on the rasterised Voronoi map). Useful for connectivity questions.\n  get_current_assignments(precinct_indices) \u2014 for each precinct, the polling place it is currently assigned to, plus the assigned travel distance. Omit `precinct_indices` for all.\n  get_assigned_site_at(x, y) \u2014 the polling place currently serving the precinct that contains coordinate (x, y).\n\nThe map is approximately 0\u201310 km on each axis, and there are roughly 80 precincts and 18 opened polling places. When you have enough information to answer, respond in the format the user requests."}, {"role": "user", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "You are examining a polling-place plan for a county with roughly 80 precincts and 18 opened polling places. No map is provided \u2014 use the structured tools to inspect assignments and adjacency.\n\nA polling place's *service area* is the set of precincts currently assigned to it.\n\nA service area is **non-contiguous** when the precincts assigned to that polling place split into two or more connected components on the precinct adjacency graph (the get_precinct_adjacency tool returns this graph).\n\nFor every opened polling place whose service area is non-contiguous, report it together with a brief reason explaining the evidence. If every service area is contiguous, return an empty list.\n\nRespond with ONLY a JSON object of the form:\n  {\"split_sites\": [\n    {\"index\": <i>, \"reason\": \"<short justification>\"},\n    ...\n  ]}\nEach `reason` should briefly state which connected components you found and which precincts populate them. Keep each reason under 40 words. Do not include any other text outside the JSON."}]}, {"role": "assistant", "annotations": [], "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_V4J826jntkk3GwQPkNSzTtIO", "function": {"arguments": "{\"opened_only\": true}", "name": "list_sites"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_RdI1s3BoxsT6X6PqGCD51lPj", "function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "get_current_assignments"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_fq7A58UkGg7RyqIsdZifvgS1", "function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "get_precinct_adjacency"}, "type": "function"}]}, {"role": "tool", "tool_call_id": "call_V4J826jntkk3GwQPkNSzTtIO", "content": "[{\"index\": 0, \"x\": 2.534889222339105, \"y\": 2.7