rea.\"}"}, {"content": "{\"split_sites\":[{\"index\":3,\"reason\":\"Orange area splits into central-south patch and isolated east-edge patch near (7.1,3.6); assignments show precincts 13,14,15,17,18,19,20,21,27,28,29 to site 3, with precinct 29 disconnected in adjacency.\"},{\"index\":5,\"reason\":\"Peach area appears in west-middle and small southwest-central patch near (0.9,2.9), separated by blue; assignments 9,68,75,79 to site 5, and precinct 79 is disconnected from 9/68/75 in adjacency.\"},{\"index\":17,\"reason\":\"Purple area splits into main northwest block and tiny far-northwest corner near (0.7,9.4); site 17 serves precincts 36,39,40,45,62,77, and precinct 77 is adjacency-isolated from the others.\"},{\"index\":25,\"reason\":\"Pink area has a mid-east band around (8.0,5.1) and a separate tiny patch near (7.6,7.2); site 25 serves precincts 25 and 38 only, which are non-adjacent.\"},{\"index\":29,\"reason\":\"Gray area splits into broad west-central block and small strip near (0.6,5.7), separated by peach; site 29 serves 48,53,54,57,59,64,78, and precinct 78 is disconnected in adjacency.\"}]}", "role": "assistant", "annotations": []}]}}
{"row_id": 54, "pair_id": "contiguity_med_18", "archetype": "contiguity", "difficulty": "med", "task": "identify", "renderer": "v2_no_markers", "prompt": "tools_only", "model": "openai_vlm_tools:gpt-5.4", "raw_response": "{\"split_sites\":[{\"index\":0,\"reason\":\"Two components: {12,43} and {21}; precinct 21 has no adjacent precinct assigned to site 0.\"},{\"index\":5,\"reason\":\"Two components: {20,28,29,30,33} and {26}; precinct 26 is isolated from the others by non-site-5 neighbors.\"},{\"index\":8,\"reason\":\"Two components: {0,6,9,10,11,13,14,15,16,18,19} and {8}; precinct 8 only touches non-site-8 precincts.\"},{\"index\":24,\"reason\":\"Two components: {35,36,41,50} and {40,44,48,53,58,65}; no adjacency links connect the two groups.\"},{\"index\":25,\"reason\":\"Two components: {34} and {57,64}; precinct 34 is disconnected from the {57,64} pair on the adjacency graph.\"},{\"index\":32,\"reason\":\"Two components: {22,76} and {66}; precinct 66 has no adjacent precinct also assigned to site 32.\"},{\"index\":34,\"reason\":\"Two components: {66,70,74} and {69}; precinct 69 is isolated from the main site-34 cluster.\"}]}", "parsed_answer": {"split_sites": [0, 5, 8, 24, 25, 32, 34], "reasons": {"0": "Two components: {12,43} and {21}; precinct 21 has no adjacent precinct assigned to site 0.", "5": "Two components: {20,28,29,30,33} and {26}; precinct 26 is isolated from the others by non-site-5 neighbors.", "8": "Two components: {0,6,9,10,11,13,14,15,16,18,19} and {8}; precinct 8 only touches non-site-8 precincts.", "24": "Two components: {35,36,41,50} and {40,44,48,53,58,65}; no adjacency links connect the two groups.", "25": "Two components: {34} and {57,64}; precinct 34 is disconnected from the {57,64} pair on the adjacency graph.", "32": "Two components: {22,76} and {66}; precinct 66 has no adjacent precinct also assigned to site 32.", "34": "Two components: {66,70,74} and {69}; precinct 69 is isolated from the main site-34 cluster."}}, "score": 0.4444444444444445, "secondary_scores": {"pred_size": 7.0, "truth_size": 2.0, "fp_count": 5.0, "fn_count": 0.0, "tp_count": 2.0, "precision": 0.2857142857142857, "recall": 1.0}, "tool_calls": 3, "tool_call_log": [{"name": "list_sites", "arguments": "{\"opened_only\": true}", "result_preview": "[{\"index\": 0, \"x\": 4.82564406285618, \"y\": 4.101284427408316, \"type\": \"library\", \"capacity\": 3000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 2723}, {\"index\": 1, \"x\": 1.6201258109703016, \"y\": 1.530988617009356, \"type\": \""}, {"name": "get_current_assignments", "arguments": "{}", "result_preview": "{\"n_precincts\": 80, \"n_returned\": 80, \"assignments\": [{\"precinct\": 0, \"x\": 2.6018983807928544, \"y\": 3.068118369625905, \"voters\": 217, \"assigned_site\": 8, \"assigned_distance\": 1.330211722650832, \"weigh"}, {"name": "get_precinct_adjacency", "arguments": "{}", "result_preview": "{\"n_precincts\": 80, \"neighbors\": [[5, 6, 7, 9], [3, 5, 6, 7, 72], [4, 5, 9, 10, 38, 75, 77, 78], [1, 5, 68, 72, 75], [2, 10, 18, 43, 49, 77], [0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 9, 75], [0, 1, 5, 7], [0, 1, 6, 8, 9, 11, "}], "elapsed_sec": 5.644674062728882, "error": "", "api_metadata": {"usage": {"completion_tokens": 338, "prompt_tokens": 12799, "total_tokens": 13137, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 0, "rejected_prediction_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 0}}, "finish_reason": "stop", "model_resolved": "gpt-5.4-2026-03-05", "system_fingerprint": null, "request_id": "chatcmpl-Ddfo7vVJfuxwxPtkOiHr5SH9Jqf2T", "n_turns": 2, "per_turn_finish_reasons": ["tool_calls", "stop"], "conversation": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are a careful analyst examining a polling-place plan for a county.  Use the structured tools below as needed to answer the user's question.\n\nTools available:\n  list_sites(opened_only) \u2014 candidate or opened polling places (index, location in km, capacity, type, opened/closed status, and current voter load if opened).\n  get_precinct_centroids(precinct_indices) \u2014 centroid coordinates in km of the requested precincts (or all precincts if `precinct_indices` is omitted).\n  get_precinct_adjacency() \u2014 for each precinct, the indices of its spatially-adjacent precincts (4-connected on the rasterised Voronoi map). Useful for connectivity questions.\n  get_current_assignments(precinct_indices) \u2014 for each precinct, the polling place it is currently assigned to, plus the assigned travel distance. Omit `precinct_indices` for all.\n  get_assigned_site_at(x, y) \u2014 the polling place currently serving the precinct that contains coordinate (x, y).\n\nThe map is approximately 0\u201310 km on each axis, and there are roughly 80 precincts and 18 opened polling places. When you have enough information to answer, respond in the format the user requests."}, {"role": "user", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "You are examining a polling-place plan for a county with roughly 80 precincts and 18 opened polling places. No map is provided \u2014 use the structured tools to inspect assignments and adjacency.\n\nA polling place's *service area* is the set of precincts currently assigned to it.\n\nA service area is **non-contiguous** when the precincts assigned to that polling place split into two or more connected components on the precinct adjacency graph (the get_precinct_adjacency tool returns this graph).\n\nFor every opened polling place whose service area is non-contiguous, report it together with a brief reason explaining the evidence. If every service area is contiguous, return an empty list.\n\nRespond with ONLY a JSON object of the form:\n  {\"split_sites\": [\n    {\"index\": <i>, \"reason\": \"<short justification>\"},\n    ...\n  ]}\nEach `reason` should briefly state which connected components you found and which precincts populate them. Keep each reason under 40 words. Do not include any other text outside the JSON."}]}, {"role": "assistant", "annotations": [], "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_AEEm7LvqyYqXSqK1Wu33WZvI", "function": {"arguments": "{\"opened_only\": true}", "name": "list_sites"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_UpiUwY9uHTie2PGWfx6lZ3lm", "function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "get_current_assignments"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_nfWRJNlNAOFpfwE4f96qxa9a", "function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "get_precinct_adjacency"}, "type": "function"}]}, {"role": "tool", "tool_call_id": "call_AEEm7LvqyYqXSqK1Wu33WZvI", "content": "[{\"index\": 0, \"x\": 4.82564406285618, \"y\": 4.101284427408316, \"type\": \"library\", \"capacity\": 3000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 2723}, {\"index\": 1, \"x\": 1.6201258109703016, \"y\": 1.530988617009356, \"type\": \"community_center\", \"capacity\": 4000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 2921}, {\"index\": 2, \"x\": 2.9122247026618164, \"y\": 1.0251496707562893, \"type\": \"church\", \"capacity\": 3500, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 3098}, {\"index\": 4, \"x\": 5.8928516858191315, \"y\": 0.4, \"type\": \"library\", \"capacity\": 3000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 2732}, {\"index\": 5, \"x\": 6.737353768790909, \"y\": 3.2255738340042597, \"type\": \"community_center\", \"capacity\": 4000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 4000}, {\"index\": 6, \"x\": 8.47333197756496, \"y\": 3.6824350551249356, \"type\": \"church\", \"capacity\": 1575, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 1509}, {\"index\": 8, \"x\": 3.903404320804744, \"y\": 2.793262925453043, \"type\": \"school\", \"capacity\": 5000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 4402}, {\"index\": 12, \"x\": 6.841826331929056, \"y\": 5.55004387021933, \"type\": \"school\", \"capacity\": 5000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 4848}, {\"index\": 14, \"x\": 2.1312960174912052, \"y\": 6.057165595848123, \"type\": \"library\", \"capacity\": 3000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 2851}, {\"index\": 19, \"x\": 3.0140178803048587, \"y\": 7.085639394499323, \"type\": \"library\", \"capacity\": 3000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 1959}, {\"index\": 22, \"x\": 7.92