{"row_id": 87, "pair_id": "contiguity_med_29", "archetype": "contiguity", "difficulty": "med", "task": "identify", "renderer": "v2_no_markers", "prompt": "tools_only", "model": "openai_vlm_tools:gpt-5.4", "raw_response": "{\"split_sites\":[{\"index\":1,\"reason\":\"Two components: {4,9} and {5}; precinct 5 has no adjacency to 4 or 9 within site 1's assigned precincts.\"},{\"index\":4,\"reason\":\"Two components: {2,7,10,67} and {68}; precinct 68 is isolated from site 4's other assigned precincts on the induced adjacency graph.\"},{\"index\":5,\"reason\":\"Two components: {0,6,13,16,17} and {70}; precinct 70 is disconnected from the rest of site 5's service area.\"},{\"index\":8,\"reason\":\"Two components: {22,23,24,26,28} and {57}; precinct 57 has no same-site adjacent precincts, splitting site 8's service area.\"},{\"index\":11,\"reason\":\"Two components: {36,46,48,51,54,58} and {64}; precinct 64 is isolated from site 11's other assigned precincts.\"},{\"index\":13,\"reason\":\"Two components: {1,8,38,39,60,65} and {72}; precinct 72 is isolated from the main site 13 cluster.\"},{\"index\":16,\"reason\":\"Two components: {35,44,45,49,55,63} and {53}; precinct 53 has no adjacency to other site 16 precincts.\"},{\"index\":18,\"reason\":\"Two components: {11,72,79} and {68}; precinct 68 is disconnected from site 18's other assigned precincts.\"},{\"index\":23,\"reason\":\"Two components: {41,64} and {47}; precinct 47 is not adjacent to 41 or 64 within site 23's assigned precincts.\"},{\"index\":25,\"reason\":\"Two components: {31,34,37,40,52,56} and {59}; precinct 59 is isolated from the other precincts assigned to site 25.\"},{\"index\":26,\"reason\":\"Two components: {42,43,59,61,62,73,76} and {56}; precinct 56 has no same-site adjacent precincts.\"},{\"index\":33,\"reason\":\"Two components: {29,32,33,66,74} and {30}; precinct 30 is disconnected from site 33's main component.\"}]}", "parsed_answer": {"split_sites": [1, 4, 5, 8, 11, 13, 16, 18, 23, 25, 26, 33], "reasons": {"1": "Two components: {4,9} and {5}; precinct 5 has no adjacency to 4 or 9 within site 1's assigned precincts.", "4": "Two components: {2,7,10,67} and {68}; precinct 68 is isolated from site 4's other assigned precincts on the induced adjacency graph.", "5": "Two components: {0,6,13,16,17} and {70}; precinct 70 is disconnected from the rest of site 5's service area.", "8": "Two components: {22,23,24,26,28} and {57}; precinct 57 has no same-site adjacent precincts, splitting site 8's service area.", "11": "Two components: {36,46,48,51,54,58} and {64}; precinct 64 is isolated from site 11's other assigned precincts.", "13": "Two components: {1,8,38,39,60,65} and {72}; precinct 72 is isolated from the main site 13 cluster.", "16": "Two components: {35,44,45,49,55,63} and {53}; precinct 53 has no adjacency to other site 16 precincts.", "18": "Two components: {11,72,79} and {68}; precinct 68 is disconnected from site 18's other assigned precincts.", "23": "Two components: {41,64} and {47}; precinct 47 is not adjacent to 41 or 64 within site 23's assigned precincts.", "25": "Two components: {31,34,37,40,52,56} and {59}; precinct 59 is isolated from the other precincts assigned to site 25.", "26": "Two components: {42,43,59,61,62,73,76} and {56}; precinct 56 has no same-site adjacent precincts.", "33": "Two components: {29,32,33,66,74} and {30}; precinct 30 is disconnected from site 33's main component."}}, "score": 0.4, "secondary_scores": {"pred_size": 12.0, "truth_size": 3.0, "fp_count": 9.0, "fn_count": 0.0, "tp_count": 3.0, "precision": 0.25, "recall": 1.0}, "tool_calls": 3, "tool_call_log": [{"name": "list_sites", "arguments": "{\"opened_only\": true}", "result_preview": "[{\"index\": 0, \"x\": 7.560530835173798, \"y\": 2.2275306374137913, \"type\": \"library\", \"capacity\": 3000, \"opened\": true, \"load\": 1896}, {\"index\": 1, \"x\": 1.7596622527422296, \"y\": 2.9963941024808656, \"type\""}, {"name": "get_current_assignments", "arguments": "{}", "result_preview": "{\"n_precincts\": 80, \"n_returned\": 80, \"assignments\": [{\"precinct\": 0, \"x\": 4.035845896147401, \"y\": 1.541373534338358, \"voters\": 329, \"assigned_site\": 5, \"assigned_distance\": 1.6200224916163473, \"weigh"}, {"name": "get_precinct_adjacency", "arguments": "{}", "result_preview": "{\"n_precincts\": 80, \"neighbors\": [[12, 13, 20, 71], [3, 8, 9, 11, 39, 65, 72], [5, 6, 7, 9, 10], [1, 6, 8, 16, 17, 22, 39, 50, 57], [7, 9, 11, 68], [2, 6, 7, 12, 70, 71], [2, 3, 5, 8, 10, 12, 13, 17],"}], "elapsed_sec": 7.4941089153289795, "error": "", "api_metadata": {"usage": {"completion_tokens": 560, "prompt_tokens": 12877, "total_tokens": 13437, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 0, "rejected_prediction_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 0}}, "finish_reason": "stop", "model_resolved": "gpt-5.4-2026-03-05", "system_fingerprint": null, "request_id": "chatcmpl-DdfrmD4hqQNzeZy1Wq4sj9PX3ajB0", "n_turns": 2, "per_turn_finish_reasons": ["tool_calls", "stop"], "conversation": [{"role": "system", "content": "You are a careful analyst examining a polling-place plan for a county.  Use the structured tools below as needed to answer the user's question.\n\nTools available:\n  list_sites(opened_only) \u2014 candidate or opened polling places (index, location in km, capacity, type, opened/closed status, and current voter load if opened).\n  get_precinct_centroids(precinct_indices) \u2014 centroid coordinates in km of the requested precincts (or all precincts if `precinct_indices` is omitted).\n  get_precinct_adjacency() \u2014 for each precinct, the indices of its spatially-adjacent precincts (4-connected on the rasterised Voronoi map). Useful for connectivity questions.\n  get_current_assignments(precinct_indices) \u2014 for each precinct, the polling place it is currently assigned to, plus the assigned travel distance. Omit `precinct_indices` for all.\n  get_assigned_site_at(x, y) \u2014 the polling place currently serving the precinct that contains coordinate (x, y).\n\nThe map is approximately 0\u201310 km on each axis, and there are roughly 80 precincts and 18 opened polling places. When you have enough information to answer, respond in the format the user requests."}, {"role": "user", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "You are examining a polling-place plan for a county with roughly 80 precincts and 18 opened polling places. No map is provided \u2014 use the structured tools to inspect assignments and adjacency.\n\nA polling place's *service area* is the set of precincts currently assigned to it.\n\nA service area is **non-contiguous** when the precincts assigned to that polling place split into two or more connected components on the precinct adjacency graph (the get_precinct_adjacency tool returns this graph).\n\nFor every opened polling place whose service area is non-contiguous, report it together with a brief reason explaining the evidence. If every service area is contiguous, return an empty list.\n\nRespond with ONLY a JSON object of the form:\n  {\"split_sites\": [\n    {\"index\": <i>, \"reason\": \"<short justification>\"},\n    ...\n  ]}\nEach `reason` should briefly state which connected components you found and which precincts populate them. Keep each reason under 40 words. Do not include any other text outside the JSON."}]}, {"role": "assistant", "annotations": [], "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_9m2Fs5hgur60ctgC0HcFWyk3", "function": {"arguments": "{\"opened_only\": true}", "name": "list_sites"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_nJH68Iovf1M3Om0wsHRhCwPb", "function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "get_current_assignments"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "call_wVfgJ0mj7sHVNbUVXxv7mB42", "function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "get_precinct_adjacency"}, "type": "function"}]}, {"role": "tool", "tool_call_id": "call_9m2Fs5hgur60ctgC0HcFWyk3", "content": "[{\"index\": 0, \"x\": 7.560530835173798, \"y\": 2.227530637